data.description: Charming 3 bedroom, 2 bath pool home located on a  large, elevated homesite!  This lovely, immaculate home boasts ample natural light, newly painted interior, and all new carpeting.  The kitchen is sure to delight with brand new white cabinetry and brand new quartz counters.  The master suite offers en-suite bath and private access to the lanai.  The interior space opens onto the spacious, screened lanai with oversized pool.  This is the perfect place to relax, entertain, and enjoy the Florida sunshine and Island breezes.  A perfect location with only 2.4 miles straight to Residents' Beach.
